  "detailed_description": "The protagonist is a girl who is looking for a way out in an unknown and melancholic world. The player's objective is to cross the scenarios. On your way there are dangerous traps and macabre beings! You will die many times! And in the most violent and agonizing ways possible. Rivers of Blood is a game of trial and error. Discover the limits of your patience and test your skills – how far can you go without dying in the attempt? Bloody and visceral game. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655610/extras/2bfa368912d84b51f28cbc132c0db7a4.poster.avif?t=1750131851\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655610/extras/2bfa368912d84b51f28cbc132c0db7a4.webm?t=1750131851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2655610/extras/2bfa368912d84b51f28cbc132c0db7a4.mp4?t=1750131851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
